		{
			dependencies: ["22C4FB700C4C7B5F"]
			description: ["Farmer's Delight cooking recipes require specific crop combinations — Vegetable Soup needs carrots, potatoes, and greens. Tomato appears in more FD recipes than any other single Pam's crop. Rice unlocks grain-based dishes and several stew variants. Each unique crop type you grow expands the pool of available Cooking Pot recipes. Prioritize crops that yield both a food item and a replantable seed — the highest-volume staples sustain themselves given enough space and beds."]
