		}
		{
			dependencies: ["F1A2B3C4D5E60001"]
			description: ["Vegetable Soup requires carrots, potatoes, Pam's cabbage, and water in the Cooking Pot. It provides six hunger bars and a short Regeneration effect — enough to replace cooked pork chops as your expedition food. Cook it in batches of six servings and stock your inventory before heading into Mine & Slash combat. At higher cultivation ranks, food buff stacking with Soul Land cultivation bonuses and M&S stat soul investments creates a meaningful composite effect that individual hunger values obscure. Feed yourself properly before every serious encounter."]
			id: "F1A2B3C4D5E60002"
