		}
		{
			dependencies: [
				"F1A2B3C4D5E60002"
				"0976ED57329E13EB"
			]
			description: ["With a diverse crop rotation, an active Cooking Pot, and real food in your inventory, the farm is established. A self-sustaining food loop removes hunger as a constraint on your playtime. The Mystical Agriculture path below extends this into passive resource generation — every ore, every essence material grown and harvested without a pickaxe. This is the base from which every expedition launches and to which it returns."]
