		{
			dependencies: ["22C4FB700C4C7B5F"]
			description: ["Your crop selection now extends beyond the starter agave — multiple food types, diverse saturation profiles, and the raw material base for cooking chains are established. This is the inflection point: the farm feeds you without constant attention. The Mystical Agriculture lane below extends the farm from food production into passive resource generation — ore essence, growth accelerators, and T2 essence that covers every basic material the pack demands without ever breaking a rock."]
