		{
			dependencies: ["0976ED57329E13EB"]
			description: ["Mystical Agriculture adds crop-form resource generation — seeds that grow essence, which converts to any base material in the game. Inferium Essence is the foundation tier: harvest it from Inferium Crops planted on any farmland type. Four Inferium Essence craft into one Prudentium (T2). Ten Inferium Essence make one T1 resource seed for a target material. Build an Inferium crop row as your base passive resource loop — it replaces mining for common materials given sufficient time and Growth Accelerators."]
			id: "F1A2B3C4D5E60007"
