		}
		{
			dependencies: ["F1A2B3C4D5E60009"]
			description: ["Prudentium Essence is Mystical Agriculture's T2 tier — crafted from four Inferium Essence, it gates Iron, Gold, Diamond, and Redstone resource seeds. It also converts to Mystical Fertilizer, which instantly matures any Mystical Agri crop to harvestable state. Reaching T2 means your farm can passively produce every standard ore type in the game. GregTech's ore processing chain exists to multiply that output — the Macerator's byproduct dusts apply to farm-grown ore essence just as to mined ore. Feed your Macerators with Mystical Agriculture output."]
