		{
			dependencies: ["F1A2B3C4D5E60008"]
			description: ["Botany Pots grow any plantable item in a compact single-block footprint — Pam's HarvestCraft seeds, vanilla crops, saplings, vines, mushrooms, and most modded plants. They require no sunlight, no farmland, and no irrigation. Soul Land spirit herbs can be grown in Botany Pots using the appropriate soil type, making them the passive indoor source for cultivation-speed alchemicals. A shelf of Botany Pots in your base runs continuously regardless of chunk loading state, producing steady output with zero player attention."]
