		{
			dependencies: ["F1A2B3C4D5E6000B"]
			description: ["The Hopper Botany Pot adds an auto-output slot that connects to hoppers and item pipes below the block. Link it to a sorted chest network via Create conveyors or GT item pipes and the pot outputs its harvest automatically on maturity — no player interaction required. A wall of Hopper Botany Pots growing Soul Land spirit herbs, each sorted by herb type into labeled chests, provides the passive cultivation alchemy supply that supports higher cultivation ranks without regular Spirit Beast Forest expeditions."]
